cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict multi-aspect sentiment ratings from reviews. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a neural model that generates probabilistic multi-dimensional masks, which is a machine learning technique, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with information retrieval and text classification, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper uses attention mechanisms and deals with image classification, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
